      <title>이재진 SBS 시청자위원장</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/people/2025/03/29/BAQDH4STMRAQJKXFQSITMH5WDY/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/people/2025/03/29/BAQDH4STMRAQJKXFQSITMH5WDY/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
      <description/>
